snippet.title: Is This Seat Taken? Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Wholesome Games Presents: Is This Seat Taken? Play matchmaker for groups of hilariously particular people in this puzzle game. Whether it’s the cinema, a bus, or a wedding, every setting introduces new characters with pet peeves that make seating them a delightful challenge! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3035120/Is_This_Seat_Taken/ #cozygames #puzzlegames #indiegames
